title.en: Imouto no Migawari de Totsuida Hazu ga, Douyara Watashi ga Shin no Seijo Datta you desu
Seijo-sama wo Osagashi de Shitara Imouto de Machigai Arimasen. Saa Douzo Otsure kudasai, Imasugu.
Denka, Anata ga Suteta Onna ga Honmono no Seijo desu
Shinigami Koushaku no Yatoware Tsuma ni narimashita ga, Kodomo-tachi ga Kawai sugite Mainichi Shiawase desu!
Saijoukyuu no Seijorashii desu ga, Ryuuou-sama no Hanayome ni wa narimasen! - Tsuihousareta no de Kusushi to shite Daini no Jinsei wo Oukashimasu
Aobara-sama ni wa Himitsu ga aru
Maou-jou no Nisemono Hime - Shujin no Migawari ni Totsuida Kyuuji-gakari ga Shokei Kaihi wo Mezashite Hisshi ni Nattara Maou-sama ni Kanchigaisarete Dekiaisareru Ken
Nisemono Seijo ga Honmono ni Katsugi Agerareru made Noso no Katei
Inchiki Seijo to Iwareta no de, Kuni wo Dete Nonbiri Kurasou to Omoimasu
Akujo Reijou desu ga, Konyakusha no Amai Oshioki ni Kanaimasen
Cinderella no Ane desu ga, Fuhoninagara Ouji to Kekkon suru Koto ni narimashita ~Migawari Outaishi-hi wa Rikyuu de Slow Life wo Mankitsu suru~
Isekai Torippushita Shinjin Shoujo Mangakka wa, Douyara Seijo ni naru you desu?!
